# Terraform
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfstate.backup
*.tfplan
*.tfplan.*
crash.log
crash.*.log

# Local override files
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json

# CLI configuration
.terraformrc
terraform.rc

# Lock files: KEEP these — they pin provider versions reproducibly
